milestones.description: de Silva has broken the record for most sixes in an innings (4) in ODIs for SL, going past Duleep Mendis's 3
Zaheer Abbas and Saleem Malik's 116-run partnership is PAK's highest for the 5th wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 95 between Javed Miandad and Qasim Umar
Roy Dias and de Silva's 96-run partnership is SL's highest for the 3rd wicket in ODIs, breaking the record of 82 between Tennekoon and Tissera
